---
description: Enforce minimal visibility for class properties and fields
globs: **/*.cs
alwaysApply: false
---

# Minimal Member Visibility

## Properties

If a property is not accessed outside its declaring class, make it `private`.

```csharp
// ❌ BAD — not used outside the class
public CancellationTokenSource? Cts { get; set; }

// ✅ GOOD
private CancellationTokenSource? Cts { get; set; }
```

## Fields

If a field is not reassigned after construction and not accessed outside its class, make it `private readonly`.

```csharp
// ❌ BAD — never reassigned, never accessed externally
private Dictionary<string, Type> _types = new();

// ✅ GOOD
private readonly Dictionary<string, Type> _types = new();
```
